claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A flowchart outlining influenza vaccination dosing for children aged 6 months through 8 years based on whether they received a trivalent or quadrivalent influenza vaccine before July 1, 2022, leading to recommendations for one or two doses of the 2022–23 influenza vaccine. does not support the claim because the figure provides pediatric dosing guidance and contains no information about Flublok, antigenic match, or WHO/FDA strain selection.
